      <title>如果日本央行债券政策令人失望，先锋集团预计日元将跌至 170</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/vanguard-sees-yen-sliding-to-170-if-boj-bond-policy-disappoints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团认为，如果日本央行本月的潜在政策变化未能提高该国债券收益率，日元兑美元汇率将面临跌向 170 的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/vanguard-sees-yen-sliding-to-170-if-boj-bond-policy-disappoints</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
